OL,6,FHe added: "Harlan had his whole future
OL,7,Fahead of him and would often speak
OL,8,Fabout marriage, children and the plans
OL,9,Fthat he had. It was also time for Deb
OL,10,Fand I to enjoy time together again as
OL,11,Fa couple. Our children were grown up,
OL,12,Findependent and have their own lives
OL,13,Fto live. This will not happen now, our
OL,14,Ftime will be helping Harlan and hoping
OL,15,Fthat he will recover more and more
OL,16,Feach day so that he can have quality
OL,17,Fof life."
