OL,3,CPassenger needs 'life-long care' after
OL,4,Cnitrous oxide-fuelled crash
OL,6,F"The aftermath of taking nitrous
OL,7,Foxide, which is a class C drug, and
OL,8,Fdriving can be catastrophic and I
OL,9,Fwelcome the sentence handed to Mason
OL,10,FThornton today, though this is nothing
OL,11,Fcompared to the life sentence Harlan
OL,12,Fand his family will now have to suffer.
OL,14,F"I hope this sends a clear message to
OL,15,Fothers, particularly young drivers,
OL,16,Fthat nitrous oxide is like any other
OL,17,Fdrug and if you inhale it at the wheel
OL,18,Fyou take a huge risk with not only
OL,19,Fyour life, but the lives of others.
OL,20,FYou will be prosecuted and put before
OL,21,Fthe courts."
